                           <p>Treatise on the art of spherical orbs (celestial and terrestrial) or ṣanʿat-i kurah in connection with the use of astrolabes 
</p>
                           <p>Work divided into several faṣl (22 in total)
</p>
                           <p>Diagrams and tables
</p>
                           <p>Colophon date may not be reliable (f. 40r): completed by Mirzā Gul Nīk the munajjim ibn Mirzā Zayn (written Badīn) al-ʿĀbidīn the munajjim, nabīrah (son’s son) of Mirzā Muḥammad ʿAlī Riyāz̤ī (or Mirzā Muḥammad ʿAlī the mathematician), on Saturday, 17 (hafdahum written as hamdahum) Jum. II 1217/15 October 1802
</p>
